Class CurrencyExchangeModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • interview.dataspark.currencyexchange.models.CurrencyExchangeModel

  • public class CurrencyExchangeModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Model created to hold each currency exchange record per currencyOfInterest wrt referenceCurrency per date. All fields are private with its associated getter/setter methods. The methods should be self-explanatory.
